{"title":"Van Dessel finds the way to adjustable reach with the new Linefinder Short Travel 29er","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/06/21/van-dessel-finds-the-way-to-adjustable-reach-with-the-new-linefinder-short-travel-29er/","date":1624289976000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>We haven’t heard much from Van Dessel Cycles in a while, but that doesn’t mean that they haven’t been busy. Instead, it looks like they’ve been hard at work on an all-new short travel full suspension mountain bike with some surprising features. Called the Linefinder, this bike may just help Van Dessel find their way back into the spotlight.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105548/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-Electric-Purple-frame.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105548/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-Electric-Purple-frame.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x320/rscb18/ng:webp/ngcb18\" alt=\"Van Dessel Linefinder full suspension bike frame\" width=\"991\" height=\"656\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105548/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-Electric-Purple-frame.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 991w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105548/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-Electric-Purple-frame-297x197.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105548/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-Electric-Purple-frame-800x530.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105548/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-Electric-Purple-frame-120x79.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105548/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-Electric-Purple-frame-768x508.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105548/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-Electric-Purple-frame-696x461.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105548/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-Electric-Purple-frame-634x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 634w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 991px) 100vw, 991px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb18 src ng ngcb18 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105548/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-Electric-Purple-frame.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x320/rscb18/ng:webp/ngcb18\" ezoid=\"0.5448582980217567\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105548/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-Electric-Purple-frame.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 991w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105548/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-Electric-Purple-frame-297x197.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105548/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-Electric-Purple-frame-800x530.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105548/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-Electric-Purple-frame-120x79.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105548/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-Electric-Purple-frame-768x508.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105548/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-Electric-Purple-frame-696x461.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105548/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-Electric-Purple-frame-634x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 634w\"></a></p><p>Van Dessel announced their latest bike over the weekend at the Bentonville Bike Fest 2021. We weren’t able to attend, so for now details are limited to what’s on their website and facebook page. It will likely be the end of the summer before the Linefinder is available, but here’s what we know so far:</p><p>Built around a 120mm travel four-bar suspension platform, the Linefinder is a full carbon frame that includes a carbon rocker with a dual-bearing conical thru axle main pivot.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105540/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-adjustable-reach-head-tube.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105540/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-adjustable-reach-head-tube.jpg\" alt=\"Van Dessel Linefinder full suspension bike adjustable reach\" width=\"767\" height=\"384\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105540/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-adjustable-reach-head-tube.jpg 767w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105540/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-adjustable-reach-head-tube-297x149.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105540/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-adjustable-reach-head-tube-120x60.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105540/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-adjustable-reach-head-tube-696x348.jpg 696w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 100vw, 767px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb18 src ng ngcb18 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105540/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-adjustable-reach-head-tube.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105540/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-adjustable-reach-head-tube.jpg 767w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105540/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-adjustable-reach-head-tube-297x149.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105540/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-adjustable-reach-head-tube-120x60.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105540/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-adjustable-reach-head-tube-696x348.jpg 696w\"></a></p><p>One of the most interesting features is housed in the head tube, which hides an adjustable-reach headset. The frame is intended to be used with a 130-140mm suspension fork, and the special headset apparently offers 10mm in reach adjustment with a large frame moving from 460mm to 470mm in reach. That headset also offers a port for the internal routing to feed into which theoretically should improve any cable rub issues that could happen from existing designs.</p><p>Geometry is said to include a 65.5° head tube angle, 75° seat tube angle, and 430mm chainstays for a large frame.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105554/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-SRAM-UDH-T-47-threaded-bottom-bracket.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105554/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-SRAM-UDH-T-47-threaded-bottom-bracket.jpg\" alt=\"Van Dessel Linefinder full suspension bike frame t-47 and SRAM UDH\" width=\"770\" height=\"378\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105554/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-SRAM-UDH-T-47-threaded-bottom-bracket.jpg 770w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105554/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-SRAM-UDH-T-47-threaded-bottom-bracket-297x146.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105554/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-SRAM-UDH-T-47-threaded-bottom-bracket-120x59.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105554/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-SRAM-UDH-T-47-threaded-bottom-bracket-768x377.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105554/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-SRAM-UDH-T-47-threaded-bottom-bracket-696x342.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105554/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-SRAM-UDH-T-47-threaded-bottom-bracket-324x160.jpg 324w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105554/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-SRAM-UDH-T-47-threaded-bottom-bracket-533x261.jpg 533w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 770px) 100vw, 770px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb18 src ng ngcb18 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105554/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-SRAM-UDH-T-47-threaded-bottom-bracket.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105554/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-SRAM-UDH-T-47-threaded-bottom-bracket.jpg 770w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105554/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-SRAM-UDH-T-47-threaded-bottom-bracket-297x146.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105554/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-SRAM-UDH-T-47-threaded-bottom-bracket-120x59.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105554/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-SRAM-UDH-T-47-threaded-bottom-bracket-768x377.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105554/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-SRAM-UDH-T-47-threaded-bottom-bracket-696x342.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105554/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-SRAM-UDH-T-47-threaded-bottom-bracket-324x160.jpg 324w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105554/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-SRAM-UDH-T-47-threaded-bottom-bracket-533x261.jpg 533w\"></a></p><p>Other details include a T-47 threaded bottom bracket with ISCG 05 mounts, a SRAM UDH (Universal Derailleur Hanger), and one water bottle mount inside the front triangle and a carbon guard on the downtube. Tire clearance is listed at 29 x 2.4″.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105544/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-cobalt-blue-frame.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105544/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-cobalt-blue-frame.jpg\" alt=\"Van Dessel Linefinder full suspension bike frame\" width=\"991\" height=\"656\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105544/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-cobalt-blue-frame.jpg 991w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105544/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-cobalt-blue-frame-297x197.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105544/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-cobalt-blue-frame-800x530.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105544/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-cobalt-blue-frame-120x79.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105544/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-cobalt-blue-frame-768x508.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105544/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-cobalt-blue-frame-696x461.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105544/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-cobalt-blue-frame-634x420.jpg 634w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 991px) 100vw, 991px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb18 src ng ngcb18 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105544/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-cobalt-blue-frame.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105544/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-cobalt-blue-frame.jpg 991w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105544/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-cobalt-blue-frame-297x197.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105544/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-cobalt-blue-frame-800x530.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105544/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-cobalt-blue-frame-120x79.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105544/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-cobalt-blue-frame-768x508.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105544/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-cobalt-blue-frame-696x461.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/21105544/Van-Dessel-Linefinder-mountain-bike-short-travel-full-suspension-cobalt-blue-frame-634x420.jpg 634w\"></a></p><p>When available, the frames will be sold in Cobalt Blue or Electric Purple, and pricing is estimated at around $6k for a bike with a Fox 34 fork and Shimano XT 1×12. Apparently large frames will be available first, with the remaining frames to follow.</p><p><a href=\"https://vandesselcycles.com/products/linefinder\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>vandesselcycles.com</em></a></p></div></div>","author":"Zach Overholt","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"7e123cda629ad2c496dcefc8bc00184742247fab01a063b19ab84edd272ceb58","category":"Cycling"}